text: Nirmala Gavit () is a Shiv Sena politician from Nashik district, Maharashtra. She was a member of Maharashtra Legislative Assembly representing Igatpuri Constituency from 2009 to 2019. ==Positions held== * 2009: Elected to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly * 2014: Elected to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly ==References== ==External links== * The Shivsena Category:Shiv Sena politicians Category:Marathi politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
